file_content.text: Hmmph. How can any live on this world? Is dead place.
These buildings... they tower over and under. No land, no water.
Is nowhere to hunt. Scorekeeper turned away from here, I think.
I like the city. It's a refreshing change from Tython.
How can you say, Herald? Look around. Is too many buildings, too much noise.
Is so. Too much noise here, too many people.
There's more to life than hunting, Qyzen.
Hunt is life. Here, though... is not so. Too many people. Too much noise.
Is no hunter's world, but I stay.
I stay for you, Herald, and for Yuon. Please--we visit Yuon first? Embassy can wait for us.
